sourcesContent: import React from "react"; import { MDBTable, MDBTableBody, MDBTableHead } from "mdbreact"; const polyStrapping = [ { productNumber: "SP-PCF3090", width: "1/2″", thickness: 0.017, breakStrength: "350 Lb.", length: "9,000′", coreDiameterHeight: "8″ x 8″", color: "Black" }, { productNumber: "SP-MP1270W", width: "1/2″", thickness: 0.027, breakStrength: "600 Lb.", length: "7,200′", coreDiameterHeight: "8″ x 8″", color: "White" }, { productNumber: "SP-MP1270Y", width: "1/2″", thickness: 0.027, breakStrength: "600 Lb.", length: "7,200′", coreDiameterHeight: "8″ x 8″", color: "Yellow" }, { productNumber: "SP-MP1570Y", width: "5/8″", thickness: 0.027, breakStrength: "600 Lb.", length: "6,000′", coreDiameterHeight: "16″ x 6″", color: "Yellow" } ]; const PolyStrapping = () => { return ( Product Number Width Thickness Break Strength Length Core Diameter Height Color {polyStrapping.map(strap => ( {strap.productNumber} {strap.width} {strap.thickness} {strap.breakStrength} {strap.length} {strap.coreDiameterHeight} {strap.color} ))} ); }; export default PolyStrapping;
